# Generic HRIS Frontend - Claude Rules

## Inheritance

This frontend inherits the root architecture rules from `../ReadMe.md`.

Do not restate or override root rules here. Only add frontend-specific rules.

## Iconography

All icons must use Material Icons from `@mui/icons-material`.

## Select `onValueChange` Null Handling

Select components may call `onValueChange` with `string | null`.

## Date Formatting Null Handling

Always handle possibly undefined/null date values when formatting.

## Type Import Paths

Import `User` from `@/types/auth` (do not import from `@/types/user`).
